Economy: ! Overall DTF in 2003-2008 is based on a different set of indicators

! For the 11 economies with population above 100Mil (Bangladesh, Brazil, China, Japan, India, Indonesia, Mexico, Nigeria, Pakistan, Russia, USA), scoring for years 2003-2012 is based on the largest business city, while scoring for 2013-2015 is based on the population-weighted data for the first and second largest business cities. Scoring for all other economies is based on the largest business city.

1. All Doing Business 2015 rankings have been recalculated to reflect changes to the methodology and revisions of data due to new information. For further details on changes, please refer to the data notes page.
